title: Hamlet - Shakespeare (BBC - Branagh, Gielgud, Judi Dench - 1992)
description:
Audio Books : General : MP3/Variable : English


Shakespeare's tragedy of a man who could not make up his mind.

This is the second of three out of print BBC recording made by the Renaissance Theater Company. 

Hamlet was recorded in 1992 and starred Kenneth Branagh as Hamlet. Also starting Sir John Gielgud, Dame Judi Dench and Emma Thompson. Music by Patrick Doyle.


Enjoy and Seed!!
